f="https://www.nme.com/artists/nirvana">Nirvana</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/soundgarden">Soundgarden</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sonic-youth">Sonic Youth</a> ）在不列颠哥伦比亚省温哥华的 Mushroom Studios 制作。然而，乐队确实聚在一起<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hot-hot-heat-announce-20th-anniversary-edition-of-make-up-the-breakdown-album-preorder-tracklist-3323803">庆祝专辑发行 20 周年</a>。</p><p> <em>《NME》</em><a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-nme-7064-314233">在一篇热情洋溢的评论中</a>称赞《Make Up...》“欢乐大胆，情感丰富”。</p><p>它补充道：“这张唱片颠覆了人们对这棵树的所有先入之见，20 年后，自鸣得意的音乐爱好者应该低声谈论这张唱片。”</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/hot-hot-heat-confirm-with-apology-sadness-and-some-embarrassment-that-their-reunion-is-over-3578165">Hot Hot Heat 的帖子“带着歉意、悲伤和一些尴尬”证实了他们的重聚已经结束，该帖子</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
格温·史蒂芬尼 (Gwen Stefani) 谈《毫无疑问》重聚：“一切发生得太快了” https://www.nme.com/news/music/gwen-stefani-on-no-doubt-reunion-it-just-happened-so-fast-3578161?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=gwen-stefani-on-毫无疑问重聚就发生得这么快Emma WilkesSat, 27 Jan 2024 16:12:38 +0000 Music NewsNewsRockhttps://www.nme.com/?p=3578161 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格温·史蒂芬妮" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>乐队将于 4 月在科切拉音乐节重聚，这是他们自 2015 年以来的首次现场表演</p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gwen-stefani-on-no-doubt-reunion-it-just-happened-so-fast-3578161">格温·史蒂芬妮 (Gwen Stefani) 在 No Doubt 重聚上发表的帖子：“事情发生得太快了”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="格温·史蒂芬妮" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/gwen-stefani-brendan-smialowski-1-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/gwen-stefani">格温·史蒂芬妮 (Gwen Stefani)</a>公开谈论了<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/no-doubt">No Doubt</a>的惊喜重聚，称这“发生得太快了”。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-features/coachella-2024-lineup-poster-talking-points-3572325">2024 年 Coachella 音乐节：今年阵容的热门话题</a></strong></li></ul><p>本月早些时候，No Doubt 宣布将在今年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">Coachella</a>音乐节上表演，这是他们自 2015 年以来的首次现场表演。</p><p>在 Coachella 的阵容发布之前，No Doubt <a href="https://twitter.com/nodoubt/status/1747393329921499505?ref_src=twsrc%5Etfw%7Ctwcamp%5Etweetembed%7Ctwterm%5E1747393329921499505%7Ctwgr%5E100a4658e7936f7e421a260244082b548b383cbf%7Ctwcon%5Es1_c10&amp;ref_url=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nme.com%2Fwp-admin%2Fpost.php%3Fpost%3D3571952action%3Dedit" target="_blank" rel="noopener">在他们的<em>X</em>账户上发布了一段新视频，</a>预告了一场重聚。这段时长一分钟的剪辑以他们 1995 年的热门单曲《Just A Girl》为背景，首先描绘了史蒂芬妮反思自己为他们的第二张唱片《The Beacon Street Collection》制作的拼贴画，然后给她的乐队成员托尼·卡纳尔 (Tony Kanal) 发短信。</p><p>然后他们与乐队进行视频通话，同意“表演”。这段视频以一个红色问号结束，最终揭晓的谜团是他们在科切拉音乐节的表演。</p><p>现在，斯蒂芬妮讨论了重聚是如何发生的。 “这一切发生得太快了，这是我最喜欢发生的事情，”她<a href="https://12ft.io/proxy?q=https%3A%2F%2Fpeople.com%2Fgwen-stefani-talks-amazing-no-doubt-coachella-reunion-exclusive-8550408" target="_parent" rel="nofollow noopener">告诉<em>《人物》杂志</em></a>。 “我认为真的只是看着互联网上的粉丝们有多兴奋？这对我们有启发。 </p><figure id="attachment_3572014" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3572014" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3572014" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270.jpg" alt="毫无疑问" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/01/no-doubt@2000x1270-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3572014" class="wp-caption-text">毫无疑问。图片来源：蒂姆·罗尼/盖蒂图片社</figcaption></figure><p>她继续说道：“这会很酷。它只是：站起来做我们一直在做的事情，那就是播放我们的音乐并尝试联系并非常感激我们获得了我们从未想过的令人惊叹的职业生涯。”</p><p>目前尚不清楚“毫无疑问”的重聚是否是科切拉音乐节的一次性演出，或者是否还有更多演出正在筹备中。 “我们还没有真正弄清楚下一步将如何做到这一点，但我们都非常兴奋，”史蒂芬尼说。</p><p>自 2012 年的全长《Push And Shove》以来，乐队还没有一起发行过任何音乐，这也是他们自 2001 年的《Rock Steady》以来的首次发行。乐队的首次演出持续了 1992 年至 2001 年，期间发行了五张录音室专辑，并发行了包括“Don&#39;t Speak”、“Hella Good”和“Hey Baby”在内的热门歌曲。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.nme.com/festivals/coachella">Coachella 音乐节</a>的其他新闻中， <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lana-del-rey">Lana Del Rey</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/tyler-the-creator">Tyler、The Creator</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/doja-cat">Doja Cat</a>均被评为 2024 年版的头条新闻。其他宣布参加音乐节的艺人包括<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/blur">Blur</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/j-balvin">J Balvin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/ice-spice">Ice Spice</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/bleachers">Bleachers</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/peggy-gou">Peggy Gou、</a> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/jungle">Jungle</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sublime">Sublime</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/deftones">Deftones</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/khruangbin">Khruangbin</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/lil-uzi-vert">Lil Uzi Vert</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/grimes">Grimes</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/le-sserafim">LE SSERAFIM</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/victoria-monet">Victoria Monet</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/dom-dolla">Dom Dolla</a>等。</p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/gwen-stefani-on-no-doubt-reunion-it-just-happened-so-fast-3578161">格温·史蒂芬妮 (Gwen Stefani) 在 No Doubt 重聚上发表的帖子：“事情发生得太快了”</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
