/watch-slash-play-guns-n-roses-use-your-illusion-deep-cut-live-for-the-first-time-3578139">Watch Slash 的后剧《Guns N&#39; Roses》“Use Your Illusion”深度剪辑首次</a>出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
